0007E1r 2               @NotSkip:
0007E1r 2  4C rr rr       jmp BasExprCmp
0007E4r 2               
0007E4r 2               ; BasExprCmp — Handle comparison: =, <>, <, >, <=, >=
0007E4r 2               BasExprCmp:
