000882r 2               ; BasCmpAuxAcc — Signed compare AUX vs ACC
000882r 2               ; Returns: N flag set if AUX < ACC, Z if equal, N clear & Z clear if AUX > ACC
000882r 2               BasCmpAuxAcc:
